VhDir Healthcare Service Eligibility

This value set defines a set of codes that indicate the eligibilty requirements for a service.

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include all codes defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/vhdir/CodeSystem/healthcareservice-eligibility
